description:
The Microsoft Visual J# Redistributable Package version 2.0 includes everything you need to run your Visual J# applications on a computer that already has the Microsoft .NET Framework v2.0 installed.

This is the "first edition" of the J# 2.0 Redistributable, published in 2006. The installed libraries are 32-bit only, meaning that on 64-bit systems they will execute in the Windows-On-Windows environment.
summary: The Microsoft Visual J# Redistributable Package version 2.0 includes everything you need to run your Visual J# applications on a computer that already has the Microsoft .NET Framework v2.0 installed.
